RegEx

Lazy Match
Lazy quantifiers:*?   +?   {n,m}?
a.*?b a123b456b matches a123b

Greedy Match
Greedy quantifiers:*   +   {n,m}
a.*b  a123b456b matches a123b456b

Look ahead
(abc)(?=.*xyz) Matches abc if there is xyz followed in the string
(?=.*xyz)abc Matches abc if xyz anywhere in the string

